data.name: TabStop
desc: This structure is used to specify a single tabulator stop.

items.name: Alignment
lines: This field specifies the alignment of the text range before the tabulator.

items.name: DecimalChar
lines: This field specifies which delimiter is used for the decimal.

items.name: FillChar
lines: This field specifies the character that is used to fill up the space between the text in the text range and the tabulators.

items.name: Position
lines: This field specifies the position of the tabulator in relation to the left border.
